You will have the ability to protect one player per matchday to prevent another manager from activating their buyout clause on them or signing them for their team.

Player scoring works based on real statistics. Follow live matches while having fun with the only official LALIGA Fantasy football game!

What are you waiting for to create a league with your friends? Manage your club by signing LALIGA's top players... And show who the best football manager is!

1. Register in the app, get a 14-player team and a 100 million budget for signings.

Prepare for fishing trip and find the best fishing times using solunar data, tide prediction, marine and weather forecast.

Fishing Points app enables you to save and find your favourite fishing and hunting locations, spots, trotlines and trolling paths. Suitable for saltwater anglers (inshore or offshore fishing at open seas and oceans) and freshwater anglers (lakes, rivers) applying various fishing techniques fly fishing, bass fishing, boat fishing, kayak fishing, ice fishing.

Know your depths, fish smarter, find and catch more with worldwide nautical charts.

Create a fishing log and save the details of every catch (photos, weight, length). Weather, sun, moon, marine, waves and tide information are added automatically.

FIND YOUR LOCATIONS
• Save fishing locations, hotspots, waypoints with 40+ new markers and 10 colours to choose from
• Record trolling paths and trotlines
• Get information and quickly locate more than 50.000 boat ramps worldwide
• Find saved locations with GPS
• Worldwide nautical charts
• Measure distances
• Set anchor location, monitor your movements and get alerted if you exceed allowed distance

FORECAST
• Daily fish activity forecast
• Best fishing times calendar
• Feeding times (major and minor times)

MARINE FORECAST
• Hourly waves forecast (waves, swell, wind waves)
• Sea temperature (SST)
• Sea currents

WEATHER & TIDES
• Current weather conditions and hourly forecast
• Wind forecast
• Severe weather alerts
• Tide prediction charts
• Barometer and hourly air pressure data
• Rain & Clouds Radar

RIVER DATA 
• Current water levels & flows for 35k+ river stations

SOLUNAR DATA
• Sunrise and sunset times
• Sun positions
• Moonrise and moonset times
• Moon positions
• Moon phases
• Almanac

SYNC DATA
• Access your saved data across all your computer and mobile devices.
• Use Webapp to plan and analyze fishing trips on your computer. Try Webapp on https://web.fishingpoints.app

FISHING LOG
• Save catches and create fishing log
• Share catch photos

SHARE
• Import kmz or gpx files from gps devices or other apps
• Share your locations with friends

Note: App uses your location for navigation, path recording and weather forecast. Continued use of GPS running in the background when navigating or recording paths can dramatically decrease battery life.

Fishbox – the ultimate fishing companion, combining interactive fish maps, forecasts, expert guides, pro expertise, and cutting-edge AI to help you land more—and bigger—fish. Whether you’re targeting bass in freshwater lakes or trolling for salmon offshore, our app gives you everything you need to plan your perfect fishing trip.

Interactive Maps & Spot Finder
 • Browse detailed bathymetric and satellite maps covering 50,000+ U.S. lakes, rivers, reservoirs, and coastal areas.
 • Filter by species, depth, structure, and access type to unearth secret honey holes near you.
 • Save unlimited “Favorites” and download offline map tiles for fishing in remote locations without cell service.

Real-Time Weather, Tide & Bite Forecasts
 • Precise hyperlocal forecasts for wind, barometric pressure, temperature, precipitation, solunar times, and tide charts.
 • Bite-time predictions calibrated for each species, based on AI analysis of historical catch data and current conditions.
 • Push notifications when conditions turn hot—never miss a feeding frenzy again.

Bait & Lure Finder
 • Discover proven baits—soft plastics, jigs, crankbaits, live bait—optimized by AI for each species and season.
 • Learn how to rig Texas, Carolina, drop-shot, and other setups for maximum hook-ups.
 • View curated “Top 10” lists from pros to stay on the cutting edge of new patterns.

Live Pro Chat & Expert Guides
 • Connect 24/7 with real-world fishing professionals for on-demand advice.
 • Access step-by-step video and photo tutorials on casting, rigging, knot-tying, and advanced tactics.
 • Master key knots—Palomar, Improved Clinch, Uni, Trilene—through interactive guides.

AI-Powered Catch Assistant
 • Ask our AI any question: “What bait works best for largemouth bass in spring?” or “How deep should I fish for walleye at dawn?”
 • Get instant, data-driven recommendations on lures, rigs, and techniques tailored to your location and target species.
 • Personalized seasonal calendars highlight peak activity windows for freshwater and saltwater gamefish.

Fish Identification & Personal Gallery
 • Snap or upload a photo and let our AI identify your catch down to subspecies in seconds.

Packed with powerful tools, Fishbox helps both novice and veteran anglers fish smarter, not harder. From precise forecasts and interactive maps to AI insights and live pro support, you’ll spend less time guessing and more time catching. Become a fishing pro with our app: conquer saltwater and freshwater, from shore casting to boat trolling. Plan like a pro with interactive maps, smart forecasts & seasonal calendars, daily AI & pro assistance, expert bait & rig tips, and instant fish ID.
